	 ('Polish Simulator',0.0,'In Polish reality, cunning and creativity matter—solve tasks in various ways, save time, and show your neighbor who''s in charge. Hunt for deals, organize barbecues, and prove that a true Pole always finds a way to make life easier for themselves and harder for their neighbor.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9brj.jpg',2025),
	 ('Cubic Odyssey',0.0,'Embark on a galactic journey in Cubic Odyssey, an open-world adventure where you explore vibrant planets, craft tools, build vehicles, and fight the Red Darkness. Uncover ancient mysteries, and shape a universe full of life, danger, and limitless possibilities!','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9ebw.jpg',2025),
	 ('E-Commerce Simulator 2025',0.0,'Build your own digital retail empire and serve customers from around the globe! E-commerce Simulator 2025 offers you a comprehensive virtual trading experience where you can showcase and sell various products.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9bgx.jpg',2025),
	 ('Escape from Duckov',0.0,'A single-player top-down looter-shooter game. Loot, escape, build, and eventually become a mighty bird soldier. Beware! If you are knocked down, items in your inventory will be lost! But don''t worry. With your infrastructure built nicely, you will rise again soon.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9ci8.jpg',2025);
